Charm_BitSet

Class AlgoCharm_Bitset

  • java.lang.Object
    • Charm_BitSet.AlgoCharm_Bitset

  • public class AlgoCharm_Bitset
extends java.lang.Object
    This is an implementation of the CHARM algorithm that was proposed by MOHAMED ZAKI. NOTE: This version implement TIDs sets as bit vectors. Note however that Zaki have proposed other optimizations (e.g. diffset), not used here.
